channel.title: Autospawn
channel.description:
Everytime I copy and paste NPC's to autospawn I get this error:
[code]Exception in thread "main" java.lang NumberFormatException: For input string: "667" at java.lang.Number.Format.Exception.forInputString <Unknown Source> at java.lang.Interger.parseInt <unknown source> at java.lang.Interger.parseInt <unknown source> at NPCHandler.loadAutospawn2.<NPCHandler.java:113> at server.main<Server.java:26>[/code]
The only time that it works is when I do it by hand I mean TYPE THE WHOLE THING. But in tuts like the traverly dungeon one tooo much typing so I need a way to fix this plz.....
